name: CatGoesFishing -Gameboy version
description:
Cat Goes Fishing for Gameboy

Inspired by the game by Cat5Games

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Play your favourite game CatGoesFishing on gameboy!

Explore the seas!

Capture and sell fishes!

Be the richest cat alive!

Controls--------------------------

Up - Up Arrow / W

Down - Down Arrow / S

Left - Left Arrow / A

Right - Right Arrow / D

A - Alt / Z / J

B - Ctrl / K / X

Start - Enter

Select - Shift

------------------------------------------

made for gbcompo21

all assests were remade and no code was reused from the original game

This game is open source(Check https://github.com/ThunderSparks/GbCatGoesFishing )
